::Shadow Wing/KitKat::

Shadow Wing:: She transformed into beast mode and flew next to 
Lunarpine."Well, shall we off then?"
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

KitKat:: She watched the wolf and owl through the trees. She drew closer to 
the ground and hid under the brush.  She could her the owl talking to the 
wolf.  She heard the other one tell the others to meet up with him and 
watched as he took to the sky.  Now the owl and wolf remain. She watched and 
listened from the shadows.

----Original Message----
>From: Yanshosh@...

>::Prowl/Ramulus::
>
>Prowl shakes his head. "Icedemon betrayed the Alliance before. I don't know
>if he'll stay loyal."
>
>He looks down at his scanner, then puts it away. "Whatever you smelled, it
>must be gone."
>
>Prowl activates his comm-link. "Ramulus, could you patrol the Ark untill we
>get back?"
>
>He turns to the others. "Let's go."
>
>With that he exits the Ark, transforms into beast mode, and flies off 
>towards
>the Cybertronian Fire.
>~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
>Ramulus nods, recieving Prowl's transmission.
>
>"We're needed back at the Ark," he says to Primal Prime, turning around to
>get back to the Ark.
